# Project Overview

This is the Kraps Storefront - a modern, subscription-based pet e-commerce platform tailored for the Estonian market. The storefront is built with Next.js 15 using App Router and Server Components.

## Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project configuration and dependencies
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - Next.js configuration
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts) - Next.js middleware for routing and auth

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router, Server Components)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Medusa JS SDK
- Stripe for payments
- i18next for internationalization
